    • Method Detail

      • generateBiomes

        public void generateBiomes(MutableBiomeVolume buffer)
        Deprecated. 
        Description copied from interface: BiomeGenerator
        Generates the biomes for the whole buffer using only biomes from the given array of available biomes. The resultant biomes are placed into the given buffer.

        The biome generator can be called multiple times for the same position. The biome generator should, for any position/world seed combination, always return the same biome.

        Specified by:
        generateBiomes in interface BiomeGenerator
        Parameters:
        buffer - The buffer to generate the biomes into.
